'''Johnny Weissmuller Jr.''' ([[September 23]], [[1940s#1940|1940]] &ndash; [[July 27]], [[2006]])<ref name="LATimes" /> was an American actor credited with portraying Card Player #2 in the [[1985]] made-for-TV film ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''.

Weissmuller also worked with Lucas when he played a Chrome Robot in the [[1971]] film ''THX 1138'' and was credited as "Badass #1" in the [[1973]] film [[Wikipedia:American Graffiti|''American Graffiti'']].

His father, [[Wikipedia:Johnny Weissmuller|Johnny Weissmuller Sr.]], is best known for his portrayal of Tarzan in twelve films made between [[1930s#1932|1932]] and [[1940s#1948|1948]]. The senior Weissmuller's performance originated the [[Wikipedia:Tarzan yell|Tarzan yell]], which [[Chewbacca]] gave in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].

